\left(1+\frac{1}{n^2}\right)^n
\log x_n
0
x_n
1
x_n=\left(1+\frac{1}{n^2}\right)^n
\log x_n = n\log\left(1+\frac{1}{n^2}\right) = n\left(\frac{1}{n^2}-\frac{1}{2n^4}+O\left(\frac{1}{n^6}\right)\right)
1+\frac{1}{n^2}\leq \exp\left(\frac{1}{n^2}\right)
\square
1\leq \left(1+\frac{1}{n^2}\right)^n \leq \exp\left(\frac{1}{n}\right)
\lim_{n\to\infty}a_n=a>0\;,\;\;\text{then}\;\;\lim_{n\to\infty}\sqrt[n]{a_n}=1
n>N\implies |a_n-a|<\frac a2\iff 0<\frac a2<a_n<\frac{3a}2\implies
\sqrt[n]\frac a2\le\sqrt[n]{a_n}\le\sqrt[n]\frac{3a}2
\,\displaystyle{\sqrt[n]x\xrightarrow[n\to\infty]{}1\;\;\;\forall\,x>0}\,
\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\square\;
\left(1+\frac1{n^2}\right)^{n^2}\xrightarrow[n\to\infty]{}e>0\implies\left(1+\frac1{n^2}\right)^n=\left[\left(1+\frac1{n^2}\right)^{n^2}\right]^{\frac1n}\xrightarrow[n\to\infty]{}1
